quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,17,"Hannde, wonkii kala yoɓete ko faggitii. Tooñe woo alaa hannde, pellet, Allah ko yaawuɗo ñaawoore"
  40,18,"Jertnirtɓe, ñalaande dillere nden, tuma ɓerɗe ɗen ƴawtirta ka konondi, hara hiɓe (heewuɓe) ngoƴo. Giɗo woo alanaa tooñooɓe ɓen, wanaa tefoowo jaɓanteeɗo"
  40,19,"Himo anndi janfa gite, e ko ɓerɗe ɗen suuɗi"
  40,20,"Allah ko goonga ñaawirta. Ɗi ɓe rewata ɗin non, gaanin Makko, hay huunde ɗi ñaawirtaa. Pellet, ko kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  40,21,"Hara ɓee yiilaaki ka leydi, ɓe ndaara no battane ado mabbe ɓen wa'unoo? Ɓen le no ɓurunoo tiiɗude doole e batteeji, ka leydi. Allah nanngitiri ɓe junuubi maɓɓe ɗin, ɓe heɓaano daɗndoowo ɓe e (lepte) Allah ɗen"
  40,22,"Ko waɗi ɗum, ko tawde Nulaaɓe maɓɓe ɓen addayno ɓe ɓanngannduyeeji, ɓe yedda. Allah halki ɓe. Pellet, ko O Doolnuɗo, Saɗtuɗo lepte"
  40,23,"Gomɗii Men nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen ɗen, e hujja ɓannguɗo"
  40,24,"haa e Fir'awna, e Haamaana, e Qaaruuna. Kono ɓe wi'i: \"Ko mbileejo, ɗuuɗuɗo fenaande"
  40,25,"Nde o addannoo ɓe goonga kan, immorde e Amen, ɓe wi'iti: \"Waree ɓiɗɓe worɓe gomɗimdimɓe ɓen e makko, accon rewɓe maɓɓe ɓen\". Pewje heeferɓe ɓen wonaali, si wanaa e majjere"